RFQ Engine Wireframe (AECS)

Purpose:
Convert visitor into engineered project definition (not contact form)

--------------------------------

[1. PROJECT TYPE]
- Ceiling system category
- Linear / Grid / Custom / Hybrid

[2. PROJECT SCALE]
- Area (m²)
- Building type (industrial / commercial / infrastructure)

[3. ARCHITECTURAL INPUT]
- Upload drawings (PDF / DWG)
- Notes from architect

[4. ENGINEERING PARAMETERS]
- Span requirements
- Load conditions
- Environmental constraints

[5. SYSTEM SELECTION ENGINE]
- Auto suggest system type
- Engineering compatibility check

[6. COMPLEXITY CLASSIFICATION]
- Low / Medium / High / Critical

[7. PROJECT VALIDATION]
- Feasibility check
- Engineering review trigger

[8. SUBMISSION ENGINE]
- Generate Project ID
- Send to engineering team

--------------------------------

UX RULE:
This is NOT a contact form.
This is a Project Definition System.
